title: Punisher: War Zone (Trade Paperback)
description:
She’s back and she wants payback. Ma Gnucci. Eighty-five pounds of hairless, armless, legless, supposed-to-be-dead evil. And that’s not the end of Frank Castle’s problems! It would appear that someone else Frank put six feet under is alive and kicking — and wants dibs on the Punisher. Enter: Elite. The seminal creative team of Garth Ennis and Steve Dillon reunites for a special sequel to their legendary story arc, “Welcome Back, Frank,” the latest offering from the red-hot Marvel Knights line! PUNISHER: WAR ZONE #1-6.
Parental Advisory …$19.99 
ISBN: 978-0-7851-3260-8
